Using Alpha channel
-> Material properties (settings)
-> blend mode - alpha blend 
-> use alpha channel on nodes


Scattering
-> add particle (hair) 
-> add new vertex groupe to object
-> go to weight paint mode 
-> add vertex group to particle system


Sculpt by Alpha
-> Brush Properties -> Texture -> New
-> Texture Properties -> open y texture 
-> Brush Properties -> Mapping to 'View Plane'
-> Brush Properties -> Stroke Method to 'Anchored'


Radial modeling
-> add plane and rotate to 90
-> add modifier 'Array'
-> than add modifier 'Simple deform' -> set 'bend' type of modifying -> set angle to 360 -> Axis to Z












